reviews.review_text: Upgrade This seems to be a slight upgrade over the more widely reviewed source (missing one cassette generation). 4.5 stars for sound...you can hear a little cassette. No comment on overall performance...I only checked out the interesting estimated.
grt wtf sugaree w/ xtra wtf like i likey

My time coming, voices saying, they tell me where to go~! Nice clean sound..I'm with (doug the dude) that 86' is somewhat passed over due to Jerry's diabetic comma..but there are some real gems in the winter/spring~ And this is one of them..this show still has some of that 85' magic to it..think how different the sound turned in 87-88 leading up to 89'~?? The Henry J Kaisers have that same magic and carry the weight for this year..SO..GIVE IT A WHIRL~Forever Grateful>Forever Dead~!!!
Good 86 Highlights:  Hell In A Bucket, Estimated Prophet, Eyes Of The World
